6
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:24,380
 Mu Dai. I'd say the portrait is quite accurate. 
   

7
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:27,230
 I'm selling the grocery store. 

8
00:01:27,230 --> 00:01:30,400
 Once I get the money, I'll take the portrait to Xiaoshang River. 

9
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,710
 Worst case, I'll ask around. 

10
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:34,770
 No way this guy stays hidden. 

